                    "effect": "You release a wave of vital energy in a 30-foot emanation . For every 10 Hit Points you are healed, you restore 1d10 Hit Points to all other living creatures and deal that amount of vitality damage to all undead creatures in the area, with a DC 37 basic Fortitude save.",
